Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========TEXT============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  天气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办演唱会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社…社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这么早就来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我们765事务所开业以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的大型演唱会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能搞起这样的演唱会了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是喜悦万分  感慨万分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还远远不止这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这仅仅是个开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}下面播报台风消息…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  话说各位偶像也差不多要来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律子她们怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们四人会从拍摄地直接过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  今天好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:00:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}「向顶峰出发！」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  弥生  快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拍我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起以前爸爸带我去音乐会的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坐在最后排的位子上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不知道台上的偶像能不能看得见最后排的观众呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的看得见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让最后排的观众和最前排的观众一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能尽情享受今天的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  一个人发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希能够闪闪发光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律子  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台风？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  我这儿可是大晴天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  我这边简直是狂风暴雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  新干线都停驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的风  人都要给吹跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雨啊  暴风雨来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}真是的  偏偏在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们会乘坐没有停驶的电车到你们那儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩排之前应该会到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:02:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  因为台风？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  虽然会晚些到达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过时间表还是照常哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  趁现在吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律子小姐她们不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步  再怎么担心也没用呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…因为紧张总是东想西想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步  这个世上存在着言灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吉利的话还是少说的好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且刚才给亚美发了邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了这样的回复  不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是「虽然台风很强  但律姐在努力  没问题」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  各位演员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想试试场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在舞台前集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能把我的音量再调大一些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道律子她们现在到什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律子  怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在到哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  车子？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车也全部停驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以租了车…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次又是爆胎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆胎…不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  彩排看来是不能参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  准备上高速  现在就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  虽然说了很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上当心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会全力狂奔过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我这超级偶像伊织不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也没法开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之路上当心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  开始彩排了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要入场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,购物的人请在这边入口排队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我一套龙宫荧光棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是律子的电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始入场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多观众哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始入场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多观众呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开演还有一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊织她们还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  大额头她们不能出场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会赶不上开演了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}四条小姐说的真发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙宫小町不在的话  情况不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观众会很失望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥  该不会要终止演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会终止的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在律子她们来之前  我们先撑住场面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（送给各位偶像的礼物请放在这里）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位观众  非常抱歉  开演时间稍有变动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将比预定推迟30分钟  于18点30分正式开演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「My  Best  Friend」之后是什么曲目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我是偶像」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这里的曲目顺序换一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…能先上这首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时制作的曲目表吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在只有这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能唱龙宫小町的「我是偶像」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希会唱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美也会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真美之后还有「START  STAR」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雪卜来唱「START  STAR」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我唱不了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始担心能不能坚持到龙宫来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我们会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  相信你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  万一不行就用我的魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然开演是这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过让我们借此机会告诉观众
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务所并不只有龙宫小町
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那些期待着这场演出的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽全力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易走到这一步的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想试试挑战下自己的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会场的各位观众  让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务所首次演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「向顶峰出发！！」即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大危机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的偶像可是都很优秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算是证明给世间看的机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缎带找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～马上就要上场了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这条围巾能代替吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  给真美了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那是雪步的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了抱歉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步  冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把化妆盒弄得一团乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观众怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  总觉得没什么热情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在才刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  律姐  这辆车就不能飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飞的话早就飞了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很抱歉  车龙一点也不动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  等下了高速公路的话  应该就不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到龙宫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开场戏是不是太长了点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然拉不上啊  雪卜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  接下来我该去哪儿来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…进程表…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  进程表借我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊  响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服都湿透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都冷静一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}真是的  突然间干什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}对不起  我想借进程表的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那也不用硬抢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美  马上要上场了  差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塑…塑料瓶的盖子不好好盖住的真也有错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}再说响总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美不能那么用力拉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子还怎么上场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  雪卜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先冷静一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来后越来越担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也搞不好要忘歌词了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得观众没什么热情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只靠我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在比起在意客人们怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如先来想想自己要向他们传达些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都是以在很多的客人面前歌唱为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今天终于能实现这个梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有点失态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要把自己能做到的传递到会场的每个角落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是这么辛辛苦苦地练习过来的  一定能传达到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  现在我们干着急也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说不定伊织她们更着急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以尽全力把我们的歌传达出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要加油了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步  裙子马上就帮你弄好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家都鼓足了干劲呢  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  如果是那个时间的应该行  嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很勉强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  制作人  能来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了  制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希的Day  of  the  future之后又是美希的人偶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是美希也不可能连续演两首舞蹈歌曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  可恶  又不能再调换曲子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两首歌只有美希一个练习过演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  虽然可能会因此坚持不到龙宫到场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跳过这首到下一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希可以试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  美希后半场的歌本来已经很多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是美希想试试看  努力一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响  真  能拜托你们伴舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制  制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  美希可能会失败哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候就由大家来一起帮忙圆场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就安心放手一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要在舞台上闪闪发光的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  High起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:15:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家因为龙宫小町没来而有点无聊的感觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊  因为台风  龙宫小町的三人迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗  但是一定会来的  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  在那之前美希我们会像龙宫小町一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比她们更卖力地表演的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睁大眼睛看着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  关键时刻了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真美发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在啊  美希美希超努力地给我们争取时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  看起来很吃力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看来能写篇好报道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的魔术是派不上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很精彩啊  美希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂  美希  没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台  非常的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  美希也有这么耀眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  春香  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像制作人说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希啊  满心雀跃  兴奋不已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯光非常的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观众的声音在美希身体里不断地回响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越想当偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在龙宫小町
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱着歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳着舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  大家呢  现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊织她们  赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  后面就交给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要准备了  我们也不能输的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙宫小町也不会输的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  第一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMOKY  THRILL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十三话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周的偶像大师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天海春香
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们765事务从下周将走向新的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.85,0:24:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  要继续关注765事务的活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
